Description: Mosaic glass inlay: pair of mosaic glass wings. On an opaque white field are four registers of feathers in purple-blue outlined in yellow. The upper edge of each wing is bordered in red and turquoise-blue. Backed on opaque red glass.
Findspot: Excavated/Findspot: Temple of Hathor (Dendara), Temple of Hathor
Bibliographic references: Tait 1991 / Five Thousand Years of Glass (pl.61)
